---
/** Pricing.astro — Una sola tarifa. Copy literal de 06. */
---
<section class="section-padding" id="pricing">
  <div class="container-narrow pricing-center">
    <h2 class="reveal">Una sola tarifa. Sin sorpresas.</h2>
    <p class="pricing-sub reveal">Beta Fundadores. Precio especial para los primeros clientes.</p>

    <div class="pricing-card card-spotlight reveal">
      <span class="pricing-badge">Beta Fundadores</span>
      <h3 class="pricing-title">Tu Oficina IA</h3>

      <div class="pricing-price">
        <span class="pricing-setup">490 €</span>
        <span class="pricing-setup-label">pago único de configuración</span>
        <span class="pricing-plus">+</span>
        <span class="pricing-monthly">97 €/mes</span>
        <span class="pricing-monthly-label">sin permanencia</span>
      </div>

      <ul class="pricing-includes">
        <li>App completa (web + móvil)</li>
        <li>Puesta en marcha guiada paso a paso</li>
        <li>Configuración adaptada a tu oficio</li>
        <li>Soporte cercano continuo</li>
        <li>Todos los bonus</li>
        <li>Actualizaciones e evolución continua</li>
      </ul>

      <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary pricing-cta">Empieza ahora</a>
      <p class="pricing-limited">Plazas limitadas cada mes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-compare reveal">
      <p class="pricing-compare-title">¿Caro? Compara:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Una administrativa media jornada: ~1.200 €/mes.</li>
        <li>Pagarle a tu gestoría por gestión completa: ~250–500 €/mes.</li>
        <li>Tu tiempo (30 horas/mes × 30 €/h): 900 €/mes.</li>
        <li><strong>KonquerAI: 97 €/mes.</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing-center { text-align: center; max-width: 640px; }
  .pricing-sub { color: var(--color-slate); margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .pricing-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-teal);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-elevated);
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.35s var(--ease-out-expo), box-shadow 0.35s ease;
  }
  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow);
  }
  .pricing-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-orange);
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .pricing-title { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .pricing-price {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .pricing-setup { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); }
  .pricing-setup-label { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-slate); }
  .pricing-plus { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-slate); margin-block: 0.25rem; }
  .pricing-monthly { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 2.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-teal); }
  .pricing-monthly-label { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-slate); }
  .pricing-includes {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.625rem;
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 320px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  .pricing-includes li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-slate);
  }
  .pricing-includes li::before {
    content: "·";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-teal);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .pricing-cta { width: 100%; max-width: 320px; }
  .pricing-limited { margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-slate); font-style: italic; }
  .pricing-compare {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: left;
    background: var(--color-mist);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
  }
  .pricing-compare-title { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-ink); }
  .pricing-compare ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .pricing-compare li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-slate);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .pricing-compare li::before {
    content: "·";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .pricing-compare li strong { color: var(--color-teal); }
</style>
